InventoryItems.Name: Lego Spongebob Krusty Krab Adventures
InventoryItems.Description:
Drive the Patty Wagon to the all-new Krusty Krab!
Dive down to Bikini Bottom for a swell time! Patrick's got the Patty Wagon all revved up and SpongeBob™ is checking out the new gadgets inside the Krusty Krab. Good ol' Mr. Krabs™ is just hoping the boys don't cause any damage!
•SpongeBob, Patrick and Mr. Krabs minifigures included! •The Krusty Krab restaurant features details like Mr. Krabs safe, money, working doors and more! •Krabby Patty vehicle also included! •Measures 6.5" (16cm) long and 4" (10cm) tall!
